  "notes": "Born June 28, 1539 in Hatton, Warwickshire — during the reign of Henry VIII. Father: John Copp (1516-1565, Hatton). Married Isabel Gunne (1550-1624, from Gloucestershire) on February 28, 1576 in Hatton. Son William Copp (1589-1670) emigrated to colonial Massachusetts. Wife Isabel died 1624 in Hatton. Died February 11, 1628 in Hatton at age 88. Buried in Hatton, Worcestershire."
